text: Kononovsky () is a rural locality (a village) in Oktyabrsky Selsoviet, Sterlitamaksky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 291 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 22 km from Sterlitamak, 6 km from Oktyabrskoye. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlitamaksky District
title: Kononovsky
